magpie.data.utilities.filters

Class ClassFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • magpie.data.utilities.filters.BaseDatasetFilter
      • magpie.data.utilities.filters.ClassFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Options

    public class ClassFilter
extends BaseDatasetFilter
    Filter entries based on value of class variable.

    Usage: <measured|predicted> <Criteria> <Threshold>
    measured|predicted: Whether to use measured or predicted class variable
    Criteria: Comparison operator used to filter data
    Threshold: Value to which class is compared

    See Also:
    Serialized Form
